data.description: Come check on this East Natchitoches 3 bedroom 2 bathroom remodeled home just steps away from Chic-Fil-A! This home features fresh paint, newer flooring, and a nice open floor plan. The living room opens into the kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. Both of the bathrooms have been updated with new vanities and fiberglass showers. The back yard is fenced and ready for your entertainment pleasure. Jump on this home before it's gone!
